# Project Structure Guide

This project is organized as follows:

- [visionspark/](mdc:visionspark): Main Flutter app source code.
  - [lib/](mdc:visionspark/lib): Dart source code for the app.
    - [main.dart](mdc:visionspark/lib/main.dart): App entry point.
    - [features/](mdc:visionspark/lib/features): Feature modules (e.g., account, gallery, image_generator, support).
    - [shared/](mdc:visionspark/lib/shared): Shared widgets and utilities.
    - [auth/](mdc:visionspark/lib/auth): Authentication screens and logic.
  - [test/](mdc:visionspark/test): Dart test files.
- [supabase/](mdc:supabase): Backend and database resources.
  - [functions/](mdc:supabase/functions): Supabase Edge Functions (serverless backend code).
  - [migrations/](mdc:supabase/migrations): SQL migration scripts for the database schema.
  - [supabase/functions/](mdc:supabase/supabase/functions): Additional Edge Functions (nested structure).
- [android/](mdc:android), [ios/](mdc:ios): Native platform code for Flutter.
- [pubspec.yaml](mdc:pubspec.yaml): Flutter/Dart dependencies and project configuration.
- [.gitignore](mdc:.gitignore): Git ignore rules.
- [README.md](mdc:README.md): Project overview and instructions.

Refer to feature-specific rules for details on each module.

